H3.text: Whose birth and death are commemorated on the same day. Shakspeare

A4.text: Miguel de Cervantes died on 22 April 1616, not 23 April 1616 as previously believed.

A5.text: The date 23 April 1616 is now understood to be Cervantes' burial date, not his death date.

A7.text: William Shakespeare's birth is traditionally observed on 23 April.
